lead_paragraph: Danny Rose has expressed regret over the "stupid" foul against West Ham United which earned the fullback a fifth booking of the season and ruled him out of Tottenham Hotspur's Premier League trip to Chelsea on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Rose Bemoans 'Stupid Foul' That Caused Chelsea Suspension
headline.main: Rose Bemoans 'Stupid Foul' That Caused Chelsea Suspension
